1
00:00:02,160 --> 00:00:08,200
[Mayor Johnson]: Spring Hill Board of Mayor and Aldermen
will come to order.

2
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:12,800
[Mayor Johnson]: Let the record show it's July 21st at 6:00 p.m.

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:17,200
[Mayor Johnson]: Let the record show that all the members
are present.

4
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:22,300
[Mayor Johnson]: We will begin tonight with Mr. Eric Drook
from Christ Chapel Church.

5
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:28,500
[Mr. Drook]: Thank you, Mayor. Let us bow our heads
in prayer.

6
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:48,200
[Mr. Drook]: Amen.

7
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,100
[Mayor Johnson]: Thank you, Mr. Drook.
Please proceed with the Pledge of Allegiance.

8
00:00:52,500 --> 00:01:10,000
[ALL]: I pledge allegiance to the flag of the United States
of America, and to the Republic for which it stands,
one nation, under God, indivisible, with liberty
and justice for all.

9
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:16,500
[Mayor Johnson]: Thank you. Next we have public comments.
Is there anyone who would like to address the board?

10
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:22,300
[Citizen Smith]: Yes, Mayor. I'd like to speak about
the proposed zoning changes on Main Street.

